title: Royal Affairs in Versailles.avi
description:
hardhun

Director: Sacha Guitry 
Writer: Sacha Guitry (scenario and dialogue) 
Stars: Michel Auclair, Jean-Pierre Aumont, Jean-Louis Barrault


Witty narration follows the history of Versailles Palace; founded by Louis XIII, enlarged by autocratic Louis XIV, whose personal affairs and amours, and those of his two successors, are followed in more detail to the start of the Revolution, after which the story is brought rapidly up to date.
